[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Changed in version 2.6: The `attribute` parameter was added.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Convert an object to a string if it isn’t already.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] This preserves a `Markup` string rather than converting it back to a basic string, so it will still be marked as safe and won’t be escaped again.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Strip SGML/XML tags and replace adjacent whitespace by one space.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Returns the sum of a sequence of numbers plus the value of parameter ‘start’ (which defaults to 0).
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] When the sequence is empty it returns start.
