[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Changed in version 3.0: Generate `https://` links for URLs without a scheme.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Changed in version 3.0: The parsing rules were updated.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Recognize email addresses with or without the `mailto:` scheme.
[src:jinja-templating/templates-p02] Ignore parentheses and brackets in more cases.
